    <item>
      <title>特鲁多面临不断上升的放弃关键气候政策的政治压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/trudeau-faces-rising-political-pressure-to-abandon-a-key-climate-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的标志性环境政策——不断升级的污染税——正日益受到攻击，因为生活成本上升削弱了公众对政府认为对遏制加拿大排放至关重要的措施的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/trudeau-faces-rising-political-pressure-to-abandon-a-key-climate-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 16:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称中芯国际如果生产华为芯片“可能”违法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/smic-potentially-broke-law-if-it-made-chip-for-huawei-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位美国高级官员表示，中国芯片制造商中芯国际如果为受制裁的电信巨头华为技术有限公司生产处理器，“可能”违反了美国法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/smic-potentially-broke-law-if-it-made-chip-for-huawei-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:54:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果未支付欺诈罚款，纽约准备扣押特朗普威彻斯特资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/ny-poised-to-seize-trump-westchester-assets-if-fraud-fine-unpaid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州在民事欺诈诉讼中针对唐纳德·特朗普的 4.54 亿美元判决已在曼哈顿郊外的韦斯特切斯特县正式登记，这表明如果这位前总统未能缴纳上诉保证金，他在该地区的财产可能面临被没收的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/ny-poised-to-seize-trump-westchester-assets-if-fraud-fine-unpaid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 13:16:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
